Congrats on the debut, album brother! You are ahead of your time and so is your vision. Got more heat in stock. 🙏🏽
Still Rollin out now! @shubhworldwide 💎

We been rollin and still rollin. Y’all ready to roll with us? 

@shubhworldwide

I’ve always been chasing the “Perfect video”. Had lots of ups and downs, but I gained a lot and I realized that it’s not the destination but the journey. After 10 years, my journey has led me to another milestone. The Ghost album. Working with Diljit Bhaji has been a dream come true. It’s so good to meet an artist who is truly passionate about the art just as much as me. I wanna thank the whole team for working with me to bringing these videos from vision to life. Your hard work truly inspires me to keep me on this path. 9/29/2023 wmk 🙏🏽
Legend talks with @diljitdosanjh Bhaji history repeated once again. 🎥

We Forever Rollin. Thank you London, UK for an extraordinary night. You guys were epic ❤️

@shubhworldwide 💎

Thank you Birmingham, UK for another phenomenal night. ❤️
